Misc scripts

- plaction.shm and plon.shm: Support files
- ntfs-expand: Expands a NTFS partition to its maximum size
- ntfs-reduce: Reduces a NTFS partition to its minimum size plus 10 percent
- mbox2sqlite.rb: Convert a mbox file to a sqlite database
- cover-fetch.py: Download covers from MP3/OGG/FLAC sources
- cover-fetch-alt.pl: (Older) Alternative to cover-fetch.py
- dump-flash-buffers: Dumps buffers from flash player (video usally) to disk
- html-compact: Compacts HTML files including external resources as base64 data
